.SH REQUIRED ARGUMENTS

-\fBinfile\fP 
grd files format name.
.PP
-\fBwindowsize\fP 
number of grids in each window in both x and y direction
.PP
-\fBsteplength\fP 
number of overlap grids in neighbouring windows
.PP
-\fBdw\fP
the interval wavenumber
.PP
-\fBwmax\fP
the maximun wavenumber
.PP
